commit message: Use applicationId and versionCode for apk baseName

Use a js callback to start loading the favicon

onPageFinished from WebViewClient waits for all external resources
(e.g. images) to load, this way the favicon gets immediately loaded when
the page is ready.
Break up HTML strings for better readability
Fix copy/paste error in log messages
Print stacktrace in onFailure for APICallback
Update CHANGELOG.md and versionCode for release 0.3
